data.description: Bring in the New Year with this Beauty! This 4-bedroom, 2-full-bath gem is nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, offering both privacy and a sense of community. On the main level, discover three cozy bedrooms, perfect for family or guests, while the upper level boasts a spacious retreat with its own bedroom, creating a versatile and comfortable living space. Granite countertops with stainless steel applicances. Newly installed LVP  flooring and fresh paint throughout. As you explore, you'll find a fenced yard, offering a secure haven for outdoor activities and pets.This residence is more than a house; it's an invitation to a lifestyle of comfort and style. Seize the opportunity to call this Polo Crossing beauty your home sweet home.
